41:31.022 --> 41:32.524
What's the point of being free

41:32.558 --> 41:34.292
if I can't go
where I want to go?

41:34.325 --> 41:36.427
Get off my ass, Heather.

41:44.903 --> 41:46.672
(sighs)

41:54.780 --> 41:57.515
